---
title: Carb Smart Crispy Chickpea Paneer Salad with Cucumbers and Honey-Tahini Drizzle
description: Golden seared paneer lends a salty, creamy bite to this fresh and bright salad. Clementine brings juicy sweetness, while chickpeas give texture and crunch!
